    My name is Olivier, I am a game developer specialising in graphics programming, 
    currently in my final year of a bachelor's degree at the SAE Institute in Geneva. 
    Passionate about real-time rendering technologies, I am looking to put my technical skills 
    at the disposal of a team to create memorable interactive experiences.
