    <br>As Lead Programmer, I was responsible for making technical decisions, assigning and managing the programming team, and building the project's code architecture.
    <br>As Graphics Programmer and Tech Artist, I created a Cel-Shader following PBR rules in post-processing in Unreal to reinforce the stylised art direction of our game, and I did most of the VFX and visual feedback.
